  <!-- Services Detail -->
  <section class="services-detail">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="service-detail-card">
        <div class="service-detail-header">
          <div class="service-detail-icon"><i class="fas fa-magnifying-glass"></i></div>
          <h2>Audit & Assurance</h2>
        </div>
        <div class="service-detail-content">
          <p>Our audit services provide independent verification of your financial statements, ensuring stakeholder confidence and regulatory compliance.</p>
          <h3>What We Cover:</h3>
          <ul>
            <li>Statutory audits under Companies Act 2006</li>
            <li>Compliance with FRS 102 and FRS 105</li>
            <li>ISA (UK) auditing standards</li>
            <li>Management letters and recommendations</li>
            <li>Audit planning and communication</li>
          </ul>
          <p><strong>Perfect for:</strong> Companies exceeding audit thresholds, lender requirements, or stakeholder assurance.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="service-detail-card">
        <div class="service-detail-header">
          <div class="service-detail-icon"><i class="fas fa-file-invoice-dollar"></i></div>
          <h2>Tax Reporting & Planning</h2>
        </div>
        <div class="service-detail-content">
          <p>Navigate UK tax compliance with confidence. We handle all aspects of tax reporting while optimizing your tax position.</p>
          <h3>What We Cover:</h3>
          <ul>
            <li>Corporation Tax planning and filing</li>
            <li>Self-Assessment Tax Returns</li>
            <li>VAT compliance and returns</li>
            <li>Employment Related Securities (ERS)</li>
            <li>Tax-efficient structuring advice</li>
            <li>HMRC liaison and representations</li>
          </ul>
          <p><strong>Perfect for:</strong> Growing businesses, corporate structures, and proactive tax planning.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="service-detail-card">
        <div class="service-detail-header">
          <div class="service-detail-icon"><i class="fas fa-book"></i></div>
          <h2>Bookkeeping</h2>
        </div>
        <div class="service-detail-content">
          <p>Accurate bookkeeping is the foundation of good financial management. We maintain clean, organized books so you can focus on your business.</p>
          <h3>What We Cover:</h3>
          <ul>
            <li>Daily/weekly/monthly transaction entry</li>
            <li>Bank reconciliation</li>
            <li>Accounts payable and receivable</li>
            <li>Xero, QuickBooks, FreeAgent integration</li>
            <li>Multi-currency support</li>
            <li>Real-time access and reporting</li>
          </ul>
          <p><strong>Perfect for:</strong> SMEs needing accurate records and real-time financial visibility.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="service-detail-card">
        <div class="service-detail-header">
          <div class="service-detail-icon"><i class="fas fa-chart-pie"></i></div>
          <h2>Management Accounts</h2>
        </div>
        <div class="service-detail-content">
          <p>Make informed business decisions with timely, accurate management accounts. Monthly P&Ls give you real control.</p>
          <h3>What We Cover:</h3>
          <ul>
            <li>Monthly profit & loss statements</li>
            <li>Balance sheets and cash flow forecasts</li>
            <li>KPI dashboards and analysis</li>
            <li>Variance reporting</li>
            <li>Strategic financial commentary</li>
            <li>Benchmark analysis</li>
          </ul>
          <p><strong>Perfect for:</strong> Ambitious business owners who want to steer by the numbers.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="service-detail-card">
        <div class="service-detail-header">
          <div class="service-detail-icon"><i class="fas fa-receipt"></i></div>
          <h2>VAT & Making Tax Digital</h2>
        </div>
        <div class="service-detail-content">
          <p>Stay compliant with Making Tax Digital while optimizing your VAT position through proper planning and timely filing.</p>
          <h3>What We Cover:</h3>
          <ul>
            <li>VAT registration and deregistration</li>
            <li>Quarterly/annual VAT returns</li>
            <li>MTD bridge software integration</li>
            <li>Partial exemption calculations</li>
            <li>Flat rate and cash accounting schemes</li>
            <li>VAT recovery strategies</li>
          </ul>
          <p><strong>Perfect for:</strong> Trading businesses, importers, and those managing VAT complexity.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="service-detail-card">
        <div class="service-detail-header">
          <div class="service-detail-icon"><i class="fas fa-briefcase"></i></div>
          <h2>Company Secretarial</h2>
        </div>
        <div class="service-detail-content">
          <p>Proactive company secretarial services keep you compliant with Companies House and regulatory requirements.</p>
          <h3>What We Cover:</h3>
          <ul>
            <li>Confirmation statements</li>
            <li>Annual returns and filings</li>
            <li>Share capital management</li>
            <li>Statutory meeting documentation</li>
            <li>Board minutes and records</li>
            <li>Companies House representation</li>
          </ul>
          <p><strong>Perfect for:</strong> Limited companies requiring comprehensive regulatory support.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
